<br>
Well someone used this line as their arguement earlier in the thread, so I'm going to use it against them.<br>
<br>
I believe they said, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> people choose a playstyle that suits themselves.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
 It must have started somewhere along the line. Some greedy bastard calls Stormfeather FFA because that way they don't have to wait in line. They chose a playstyle that suited themself. <br>
<br>
Stormfeather is not a random mob is has a static spawn point and timer. If it is a FFA mob why do you see people CAMPING him in the same spot every time? <br>
<br>
If YOU saw someone waiting at SF's spawn would you ignore the person and wait until it spawned, and then move in for the kill?<br>
<br>
I have a better analogy than the others posted here, and this one actually comes from everquest, not real life.<br>
<br>
Say you are a lvl 10 paladin hunting in east commons. You attack a darkweed snake and when it's almost dead a zombie aggroes you. Since you're near the tunnel you shout for help. A lvl 12 cleric stands by, waiting for you to die so they can finish off the snake and get the exp. <br>
<br>
Tell me you wouldn't be pissed off if something similar happened to you. This is very similar to what happened to Gun. <br>
<br>
He was fighting stormfeather, a cougar aggroed on him. He reached a point where he knew he was going to die. He asks Razer to please not loot the map piece. The poor guy would have killed Stormfeather if not for the cougar probably. <br>
<br>
Crypte sees all of this. And like the lvl 12 cleric he waits until Gun drops, and then knowing he has to compete with Razer now, uses his disc to kill the mob quickly and clear out. <br>
<br>
I want to see any one of you who are defending crypte wait at a camp for umpteen hours and then as soon as your mob appears have someone roll by and take it out. Tell me you would not be pissed and you are proclaiming yourself a LIAR. <br>
<br>
Crypte is an ass plain and simple, if you fail to see this then you sir, are blind.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=theloneranger>The Lone Ranger</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.home.net/arabprince/icon57.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 554<br> <font color=#E9D756>(9/20/02 10:47:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3634.topic&index=122>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> !</span><hr size=1> Sig did not show on my above post. Just wanted to leave my name at the bottom.<br>
